race.comment: GAWLER GIRL RUBY (1) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished third (16.33) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Solid record here winning three races. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from six attempts. Top chance in this line up. MYALL CLYDE (2) jumped from this box and scrambled home to a narrow Other win at Hobart over 461m latest (26.58). Bold showing expected again. RUBEN RHODE (8) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at Hobart over 461m behind Push The Button (26.66) in a Grade 5. Form from his last run is proving strong. Worth another chance. Something for the Multiples: BUCKLE UP AMANDA (6)
